                Alternatively, the input upload is also available. Sequences submitted without the secondary structure
                are folded with the RNAfold program (Lorenz et al., 2011). The RNA molecules have to be at least 3
                nucleotides long, and shorter than 3000. At most 100 sequences can be submitted.<br><br>
